The Java code's GCD:

public static int gcd(int a, int b) {

    int tmp;

    if (b > a) {

        tmp = a;

        a = b;

        b = tmp;

    } if (b == 0) {

        return a;

    }

    int r = -1;

    do {

        r = a % b;

        a = b;

        b = r;

    } while (r != 0);

    return a;

}

So the loop continues until r is 0.

